          "summary": "24/2017 When we look at major division of food and non -food commodities, which holds large share in the commodity basket, the magnitude of Food and Non -alcoholic beverages inflation rate at June EFY2017 showed 11.7% as compared to the same month in the previous year. From Food and Non -Alcoholic Beverage aspect, the highest weight is hoed by Bread and Cereals, Vegetables, Other -Food products, Non -Alcoholic Beverage, and Meat; whose inflation at June EFY2017 is recorded  a constant for Bread & Cereals (0.0%); Vegetables (14.9%); Other -Food products (Food products not elsewhere classified) (18.8%); Meat (12.0%) and Non -Alcoholic Beverages & coffee (47.4%) .",
